title: Casey Anthony’s parents: What they really think about Tot Mom

description:
George and Cindy Anthony have suffered through unbearable torture as the parents of Casey Anthony. They give their most revealing interview yet about their thoughts on their daughter in “Casey Anthony: An American Murder Mystery.” Nancy Grace and Alan Duke discuss what they say in the Investigation Discovery’s series in this episode.
